node.text: That Molly slaying that #buttercream today in studio! Head over and follow us on TikTok to see so much behind the scenes action from our shops!! #whiteflowercakeshoppe #buttercreamcake #buttercreamflowers #cleveland

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 06, 2021. May be an image of dessert.

node.text: It’s a great day for a Mocha Macaron! Both shops open for walk in today see you soon! Photo by @balsam_bill_hikes #whiteflowercakeshoppe #macarons #cleveland

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 05, 2021.

node.text: Molly designed the CUTEST succulent and cactus #buttercream sugar cookies and they are available today at both locations! 🌵💕#whiteflowercakeshoppe #cookies #sugarcookies #cleveland

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 04, 2021. May be an image of dessert.

node.text: Chocolate Caramel layer crisp bars are in the case today!😱😱 This incredible layered dessert designed by Bill and Molly will have your taste buds swooning🤤🤤 Layers of Marshmallow crisp, Chocolate Brownie, Caramel buttercream and Chocolate mousse are dipped in a dark chocolate glaze...YUM!! Both shops open for walk in today, Beachwood 11-6, Solon Noon-6 #whiteflowercakeshoppe #brownie #buttercream #cleveland photo by @balsam_bill_hikes

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The White Flower Cake Shoppe on August 03, 2021. May be an image of cake.

node.text: Kelly came up with some hilarious new words cakes!Tag your sarcastic cake loving friends for a laugh🤣🤣🤣 List any other messages you think we should add to this collection below👇🏻#whiteflowercakeshoppe #instacake #buttercream #cleveland photos by @balsam_bill_hikes
